  "text": "The synaptic rearrangement described in the present study, is in line with, and significantly extends, previous findings [CITATION_1] and could also be a key factor in the down regulation of CB1 receptors after THC-withdrawal [CITATION_2] , as well as the CB1-mediated inhibition of excitatory synaptic transmission at the excitatory synapses between the prefrontal cortex and the NAcc [CITATION_3] .",
